            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "__init__ 方法是直譯器在建立物件時自動執行的特殊方法，通常用來設定初始的屬性（如：身高、攻擊力、血量）。"
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "self 代表「物件本身」。以 class dog() 為例，建立物件 Lucky = dog() 後，每個方法中的 self 就相當於 Lucky，藉此設定和存取屬性。"
            },
            {
              "type": "animation",
              "animationId": "self-binding",
              "caption": "self 如何綁定到具體的物件實例",
              "steps": [
                "定義 class Dog 與 __init__(self, name)",
                "呼叫 Lucky = Dog(\"Lucky\")",
                "self 自動綁定為 Lucky",
                "self.name 等同 Lucky.name"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "code",
              "language": "python",
              "code": "class Dog:\n    def __init__(self, name):   # 自動執行一次\n        self.name = name        # 設定屬性\n        self.hp = 100\n    \n    def bark(self):             # self = 物件本身\n        return f\"{self.name} says Woof!\"\n\nLucky = Dog(\"Lucky\")           # self → Lucky\nprint(Lucky.bark())            # Lucky says Woof!\nprint(Lucky.hp)                # 100"
            },
            {
              "type": "diagram",
              "diagramId": "class-blueprint",
              "caption": "Class（藍圖）→ __init__ + methods + properties → Object（實體）"
